---
<section class="contact-cta" id="contact">
  <div class="container cta-inner">
    <div class="cta-text">
      <span class="section-label">Ready to Visit?</span>
      <h2 class="cta-title">Come Hungry. Leave Happy.</h2>
      <p class="cta-sub">
        Enrico's Tacos is open late — Monday through Saturday until 1 AM.
        Whether you're craving birria at midnight or looking for a spot
        after a long day, we've got you.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="tel:+17274095348" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">📞 Call (727) 409-5348</a>
      <a
        href="https://maps.google.com/?q=916+Patricia+Ave+Ste+D,+Dunedin,+FL+34698"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg"
      >📍 916 Patricia Ave Ste D, Dunedin</a>
      <a
        href="https://www.yelp.com/biz/enricos-tacos-dunedin"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="btn btn-yelp btn-lg"
      >★ See Us on Yelp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--clay) 0%, #6b1e06 100%);
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .contact-cta .section-label {
    color: var(--amber-light);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    color: var(--crema);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .cta-sub {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .btn-lg {
    padding: 0.9rem 1.8rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
